<paragraph blockId="35.[189,1399,618,789]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
This species was described based on a single female specimen collected by Wilmatte P. Cockerell in southern 
<collectingCountry box="[297,351,655,681]" name="Peru" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Peru</collectingCountry>
on August 22. The 
<typeStatus box="[582,685,654,680]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">holotype</typeStatus>
is housed at 
<collectionCode box="[836,926,654,680]" country="USA" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34925" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34925" name="American Museum of Natural History" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">AMNH</collectionCode>
and has the following data label: Tingo. 
<collectingCountry box="[189,247,691,717]" name="Peru" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Peru</collectingCountry>
. Aug. 22. (W.P.Cockerell) [handwritten]\ 
